# Simple Chat Messaging System (Microservices + Kafka)

## Services
- API Gateway (Express + Socket.io) :4000
- User Service (JWT + bcrypt + SQLite) :4001
- Message Service (SQLite + Kafka Producer) :4002
- Analytics Service (Kafka Consumer + /stats) :4003
- Kafka + Zookeeper (Docker)

## Run
1. Install Docker + Docker Compose
2. From project root:
   ```bash
   docker compose up --build
